<command>gambit-nfg-lp</command> reads a two-player constant-sum
strategic game on
standard input and computes a Nash equilibrium by
solving a linear program.
</para>

</refsect1>

<refsect1>
<title>OPTIONS</title>
<variablelist>
<varlistentry>
<term><option>-d </option><replaceable class="parameter">DECIMALS</replaceable></term>
<listitem>
